{"tid":2193170,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"請珍惜快必...（認真）","createTime":"2020-09-07T15:16:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T04:03:37.000Z","uid":53062,"like":51,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8e558f8b7c00eb6553b82378171efddefcd21e21","tid":2193170,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T15:16:49.000Z","msg":"細個開始上高登果陣好拎憎人民力量，覺得毓民、皇上、燒山好拎嘈（當年選舉論壇燒山俾人話講粗口跳晒掣），次次辯論都好似鬥大聲好悶<br />\n<br />\n到佢地退晒休，先知果D老練既技術／論述係好野黎<br />\n<br />\n皇上既獨特駁論、毓民（全盛時期）既引經據典、燒山對陶傑既執著，都係到退休／收左皮先發現佢地原來咁拎勁<br />\n<br />\nLihkg仔好多人都反快必，但係老實講佢既唱聖詩技術、教人踢保能力、對D7689既執著，冇人比得上佢（我覺得依家慢必&gt;&gt;快必）<br />\n<br />\n我諗快必好大機會言論煽動罪成，其實睇得1場官司得1場官司，好好珍惜<br />\n<br />\n利申：高登年代熱民公民迷"},{"pid":"876a1e3cb5ebd17d2d921c3ba4e7181a9409efa1","tid":2193170,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T15:19:02.000Z","msg":"仲有陳雲"},{"pid":"ae1062017265298743f632880a929a1322279f48","tid":2193170,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T15:26:36.000Z","msg":"而家轉左咩會？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e94eb9261c9fd9b7e69ce1b78b6b8e07be571d50","tid":2193170,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae1062017265298743f632880a929a1322279f48","tid":2193170,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T15:26:36.000Z","msg":"而家轉左咩會？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T15:39:23.000Z","msg":"而家許智峯迷"},{"pid":"13ed4ca807596182c02f9aa269af4947597382a3","tid":2193170,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e94eb9261c9fd9b7e69ce1b78b6b8e07be571d50","tid":2193170,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae1062017265298743f632880a929a1322279f48","tid":2193170,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T15:26:36.000Z","msg":"而家轉左咩會？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 