,{"pid":"0f495cfdfa895aa520bdd6023c81ee33356c4a10","tid":2193170,"uid":183058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T16:11:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"360659b948765af746c3a27ab773e4c10a66901b","tid":2193170,"uid":265731,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T16:12:01.000Z","msg":"佢地嘅口才、破格同勇氣的確摑醒咗好多傳統泛民支持者，以至今日嘅勇武同攬炒派嘅誕生係應記一功，只係毓民嗰啲放唔低舊時恩怨，熱狗更加不提也把<br />\n<br />\n希望起碼夠人喺國際線聲援快必<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4649da975dbbad461fd2de9bb5381144d3a11a6c","tid":2193170,"uid":33642,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T16:17:45.000Z","msg":"快b份人有時就係太直<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />初選論壇嗰就係咁，幾唔認同本民前嘅立場都好，學人up句光時出嚟留住班fans咪得，係都要去到咁行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />懷念c君"},{"pid":"cc89079021e9f16c04ddaabba7618e2bf0ffebff","tid":2193170,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T03:37:08.000Z","msg":"過咗48小時仲未有得過堂，擺明玩佢之前教人一係過堂 一係無條件釋放<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"391b708a759cc655aa915929b131a70f34f848af","tid":2193170,"uid":127176,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T03:56:59.000Z","msg":"提當年人力班人做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家人力同當年主流果班根本唔啱key"},{"pid":"dc15c410c6495fc2057ad9d9527eb2f40e1408e2","tid":2193170,"uid":284671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T04:05:25.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n所有手足都一樣"},{"pid":"edc87196a767600aae0a22721ed1cb872387d83a","tid":2193170,"uid":127176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T05:37:58.000Z","msg":"上年佢做蘋果四點鐘睇住警謊開live chat嘅常客，我果陣開始留意佢，佢講嘢風格同其他政治人物真係唔同d，包括佢拍檔慢必同一班後生抗爭派，唔鍾意嘅會覺得佢唔正經，但聽佢屌黑警屌港共係好痛快<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好多連登仔只夠膽用鍵盤打嘅說話佢可以一個人當街嗌出嚟<br />\n<br />\n有d人話佢唔適合做議員，但我正正覺得立法會先最需要佢呢d口若懸河又火爆唔顧形象嘅人，比佢入到去應該仲搏過慢必，今時今日議政能力已經唔係最重要，更何況我以我之前聽佢D100同街站片段唔覺得佢論政唔掂"},{"pid":"bbcb8f7d4397ba136e48be344443ee5a6fcc8247","tid":2193170,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T09:48:58.000Z","msg":"#ALERT 譚得志被控五項發表煽動文字罪及一項公眾地方作出擾亂行為罪，在粉嶺裁判法院提堂，不准保釋 (9/8/17:38)<br />\n<br />\n冇得保釋，痴Q線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4941fc3a5ee6bc83377dfc4ea9621199f604d3f7","tid":2193170,"uid":30476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T12:10:17.000Z","msg":"點先救到C君<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7ee6a3739c2ed8084972469c901fd8e2af54933","tid":2193170,"uid":304090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T12:13:48.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"4bf79e0f1f745836e443b8e4ff34ecddbfd89dd5","tid":2193170,"uid":268373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T12:19:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef9da116f26f9a7955829b19f36c9e11728749a0","tid":2193170,"uid":268373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T12:19:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"